274
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:43,590
Step forward.

275
00:16:44,540 --> 00:16:45,580
C'mon.

276
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:52,260
You're from that time?

277
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:54,630
You came here to get killed?

278
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,590
Kill him!

279
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:58,960
Kill him! Kill him!

280
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:02,780
Kill him! Kill him!

281
00:17:02,830 --> 00:17:04,940
I came to bring Baji-kun back.

282
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,349
