283
00:17:11,859 --> 00:17:17,910
One of Toman's founding members
and the 1st Squad Captain, Keisuke Baji!

284
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:22,579
He claims he wants to abandon
Toman and join Valhalla!

285
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:26,300
One of Toman's top-brass
wants to join Valhalla?

286
00:17:26,329 --> 00:17:27,460
Ain't that bad?

287
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,180
No, this is a huge deal.

288
00:17:29,610 --> 00:17:30,890
Indeed!

289
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:33,180
This is a very serious matter!

290
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:38,770
Enlisting Baji will aid us
greatly in crushing Toman!

291
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,710
But!

292
00:17:40,730 --> 00:17:44,570
We must first solve just
one remaining problem.

293
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:49,640
He might be one of Toman's spies!

294
00:17:51,150 --> 00:17:55,290
So I had Kazutora
prepare a witness for us!

295
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:59,500
I will now summon the witness forward!

296
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:05,410
Takemichi Hanagaki.

297
00:18:05,570 --> 00:18:07,290
Y-Yes?

298
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:13,140
What did Baji over here say in
front of everyone at Toman's gathering?

299
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:15,190
Well..

300
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,720
"I'm joining Valhalla."

301
00:18:17,740 --> 00:18:19,390
"Toman is my enemy."

302
00:18:19,410 --> 00:18:20,850
That's what he said.

303
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,890
Kazutora, what do you think?

304
00:18:25,610 --> 00:18:27,820
"Loyalty test" and "Witness summon."

305
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:29,930
I think that's good enough.

306
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:32,570
We can use Baji in a fight.

307
00:18:32,870 --> 00:18:35,670
