Toman while I was away.

308
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,880
I believe it's worth
letting him join Valhalla.

309
00:18:41,930 --> 00:18:43,390
Are you sure, Baji?

310
00:18:43,910 --> 00:18:45,930
We will crush Toman.

311
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:47,750
And then...

312
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:50,340
We'll kill Mikey.

313
00:18:54,910 --> 00:18:55,910
Yeah.

314
00:18:58,130 --> 00:18:59,840
I'll help you with that.

315
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,960
Kazutora.

316
00:19:02,470 --> 00:19:04,590
That's enough, right?

317
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,790
Okay!

